response.overview: When athletic teen Mari Collingwood opts to hang out with her friend Paige in town rather than spend an evening in with her parents vacationing at the family's remote lake house, it marks the beginning of a night no one is going to forget.
response.tagline: If bad people hurt someone you love, how far would you go to hurt them back?
